Package net.juniper.smgt.ssp.model

Interface Summary
PortalBehavior The portal behavior specifies the functionality of the "model" used to interface with a Service Activation Engine.
 

Class Summary
CableBehavior Implementation of the "Cable Behavior" The Cable Behavior allows users which do not have physical interfaces to connect to the SAE
EquipmentRegistrationBehavior Implementation of the "Equipment Registration Behavior".
GenericPortalBehavior Generic implemenation of the PortalBehavior.
ISPServiceBehavior Implementation of the "ISP Service Behavior" (previously known as "Normal Behavior".
PortalUtil Utilility for converting CORBA object and Portal objects.
Row Wrap information read from a remote Service Activation Engine.
UserInfo Wrap information about the user session attached to the current request.
UserInfo.Values Encapsulate the "values" of user attributes read from the remote Service Activation Engine.
